{"tid":1693344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太古保安室是有盾和防暴棍有足夠能力保護市民","createTime":"2019-11-04T14:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T15:31:06.000Z","uid":290594,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"760aea90faac0d9d56256f6a0552bffd121e8f60","tid":1693344,"uid":290594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"利申：我曾經在太古城做過保安<br />\n而佢哋保安休息室在港島西乜乜個頭<br />\n入面有足夠工具保護市民同居民<br />\n但佢哋無咁做，而平時佢哋工作都已經好hea<br />\n所我先離職，但係我記得好清楚<br />\n佢哋係有足夠能力，例如防暴盾、防暴棍<br />\n而點解佢哋唔咁做係因為事不關自姐"},{"pid":"a70175bed742bc6fc9111e262f46e9a1efc98a33","tid":1693344,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"想保住份工而又有罷工效果？輪更制幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樽頸？攬炒？不如試下輪更啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"467ec710deb8bac5761189cdbaaabc9e160a0349","tid":1693344,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"2e5176f1d3dad1f1f5c1271796b4d80e183957af","tid":1693344,"uid":92908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:18:13.000Z","msg":"如果香港每個人都真係緊守自己崗位<br />\n今日一定唔會變成咁"},{"pid":"b34ee3837e6e428eb3444217ab3d526dd2738efe","tid":1693344,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"有冇在職人士"},{"pid":"9efd94e8ee2054479a51d266c73367d1318ac78c","tid":1693344,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"有鎗都冇用<br />\n俾你做<br />\n你會唔會攞枝鎗指撚住popo唔俾佢哋入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2289ec22c3b6f89e6c48afae23324624b1